✨NEW GIVEAWAY ALERT✨

It's time to upgrade your style game to the next level! Cases - on us, participation - on you 👀 3 lucky winners will have an opportunity to win 3 cases of their choice 🤳 How cool is that?

HOW TO ENTER:
1. Follow @burgaofficial
2. Like our 5 recent posts ❤
3. Comment the name of your favorite BURGA design (for example, Almond Latte or Summer Scent, and tag your bestie (emoji) 👯‍♀️

Giveaway starts at 15:00 (GMT+2) 28/07/21 until 18:00 (GMT+2) 04/08/2021. International giveaway, 14+ y.o participants only. 3 winners will be selected randomly and mentioned there. Odds of winning depend on the total number of entries received.
